---
title: Family-Style Summer Chili Nachos with Kidney Beans and Tortilla Chips
description: Gooey cheese, tender veggies and warm tortilla chips are the perfect combo for these summer chili nachos! Bright and fresh lettuce is the perfect topping for this flavour packed beef mixture. It adds the perfect amount of zip and crunch. Dig in and enjoying dinner tonight, family style!
